  "body": "### Description\n\nWhen running in dev mode it would be nice if new Flyway migration scripts (along side any existing migration scripts under `src/main/resources/db/migration`) would be detected and then executed when the user presses the _Migrate_ button in the Flyway Dev UI.\r\n\r\nCurrently adding a new migration script and pressing _Migrate_ has no effect. The application must be explicitly restarted (e.g. pressing `s` in the console).\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
